ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84a3ef235c92ecf17ae19315dcfeb714c3f9f40","tid":713252,"uid":36497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T16:57:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=SP&amp;message=5236240&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DSP%26message%3D5236240%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=gPG8u%2BcTOjN0AfjFGLeD0zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d741f078\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=SP&amp;message=5236240&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n<br />\n尼馬 我當你一秒球皇 <br />\n尼馬 我當你一世球皇 <br />\n廢特 打前鋒真係特廢 <br />\n祖奧 時時其實還廢 <br />\n雷斯 根本係一個炸彈 <br />\n施華 冇左你真係唔掂 <br />\n施薩 雙拳難敵四手 <br />\n史高拉利 比人炒七比零 <br />\n零二巴西 大哨細哨李華度都不夠 <br />\n佢有奪冠過你有沒有 <br />\n尼馬施華冇左就會輸波 <br />\n雷斯拍住丹迪 <br />\n俾人中出7連發 <br />\n實實在在輸過次七比一 <br />\n每一分鐘都 被入一球 <br />\n尼馬 與施華 無得出就無隊型 <br />\n好彩德國放水一球 <br />\n美斯散步帝 確是散步帝 <br />\n阿古路同希古恩 唔知踢乜鳩 <br />\n全靠散步帝 場場都 出散步神功 <br />\n柏拉斯奧拿維斯 真係好屎波 <br />\n垃圾隊友 踢一人球隊 <br />\n仍然好撚勁 是今日 完全唔走位"},{"pid":"d474580bd474ed57cdfab20cb332fd0a56ebde17","tid":713252,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63f71e4ba4cc63ca2ac45599a181ee34427b926a","tid":713252,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T16:34:16.000Z","msg":"尼馬 我當你一秒球皇<br />\r\n尼馬 我當你一世球皇<br />\r\n耶穌 打前鋒真係特廢<br />\r\n古仔 時時其實還廢<br />\r\n<br />\r\n有冇巴打接落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 $100呢<br />\n普京成功黑走西班牙 此post一人派100<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/725127/40?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/725127/40?